transcripts.text: Hello, family.  I would like to invite you out to our upcoming conference.  Stephen Dorby Ministries will be holding a one-day conference Saturday, November the 2nd, 2019.  The conference will be held at the BWI Airport Marriott, 1743 West Nursery Road, Linthicum, Maryland.  Registration is $25 and children 12 and under are free.  We will be breaking Destiny Ministries band and praise team, and I will be ministering the word.  It's a blessing to fellowship with and to meet our brothers and sisters at each conference.  To register, please go to stephendorbyministries.com for more information.  Be blessed.
